
| Field         | Type     | Required | Description                         |
|---------------|----------|----------|-------------------------------------|
| userId        | ObjectId | Yes      | Reference to User                   |
| title         | String   | Yes      | Task name                           |
| description   | String   | No       | Task details                        |
| category      | String   | No       | Category e.g. Work, Personal        |
| priority      | String   | No       | Low, Medium, High                   |
| dueDate       | Date     | Yes      | When task is due                    |
| reminderSet   | Boolean  | No       | Whether reminder is enabled         |
| isCompleted   | Boolean  | No       | Task status                         |
| createdAt     | Date     | Auto     | Auto created timestamp              |
| updatedAt     | Date     | Auto     | Auto updated timestamp              |

## Example:
```group
{
  "title": "Submit Final Report",
  "priority": "High",
  "dueDate": "2025-07-31",
  "isCompleted":Â false
}
